movie.title: Soof
movie.writer: Marjolein Beumer (screenplay), Marjolein Beumer (story), Marjolein Beumer, Sylvia Witteman (column)
movie.actors: Lies Visschedijk, Fedja van Huet, Daniel Karaty, Lobke de Boer
movie.plot: Soof is reaching 40 and has everything she ever wanted: three children, a small catering business, a sweet husband Kasper and a lovely home. Until she starts asking herself: 'is this all there is'?
